            <origDate instant="false">Acta sunt hec Patavie in curia celarii venerabilis capituli
               Pataviensis, anno, indictione, mense, hora et pontificatu predictis, presentibus
               ibidem discretis viris Michaele Zeler de Traunstain et Achacio Siechreuter, clerico
               et laico litterato, Salczburge </origDate></creation></profileDesc></teiHeader><facsimile><surface><graphic url="http://images.monasterium.net/pics/AT-WStLA/HA-U/WStLA-HA-Urkunden_03637_r.jpg"/></surface><surface><graphic url="http://images.monasterium.net/pics/AT-WStLA/HA-U/WStLA-HA-Urkunden_03637_v.jpg"/></surface></facsimile><text><body><div type="abstract" resp="kg"><p>* <rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_II_3637">Anno nativitatis ( domini) millesimo
                  quadringentesimo quinquagesimo quinto, indiccione tercia, die vero secunda mensis
                  augusti, hora terciarum vel quasi, pontificatus sanctissimi in Christo patris et
                  domini nostri, domini Calisti, divina providencia pape tercii, anno primo ,
                     <triggerstring n="disp">bestellt</triggerstring>
                  <rs type="fn" role="issuer"><rs type="person" ref="pe__konrad_sachs_QGW_II_II_3637">Conradus Sachss, <roleName type="prof">presbyter</roleName> Pataviensis diocesis</rs>,</rs>
                  <triggerstring n="disp">zu Procuratoren</triggerstring> in Angelegenheit der ihm <rs type="fn" role="other">von dem <rs type="person" ref="pe__ulrich_QGW_II_II_3640">Passauer <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__passau-dioezese">Bischofe</roleName> Ulrich</rs>
                     <triggerstring n="fn">gestatteten</triggerstring>,</rs>
                  <rs type="fn" role="other">an <rs type="org" ref="org__wien-st_agnes_auf_der_himmelpforte">die Priorin des
                        Himmelpfortklosters in Wien</rs>
                     <triggerstring n="fn">zu richtenden ersten Bitte</triggerstring></rs>
                  <rs type="fn" role="recipient">die <rs type="person" ref="pe__johann_hausner_QGW_II_II_3637"><roleName type="prof">Magister</roleName> Jodocum Hausner, Decretorum <roleName type="prof">doctorem</roleName>, <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__niedernkirchen-pfarre"><add>Pfarrer</add></roleName> in
                        Niedern sand Johanns kirchen</rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pe__johann_goldner_QGW_II_II_3237"><roleName type="prof"><add>Magister</add></roleName> Johannem Goldner, <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__retzbach-pfarre"><add>Pfarrer</add></roleName> in Reczpach,
                        et <roleName type="prof"><add>Magister</add></roleName></rs>
                     <rs type="person" ref="pe__christoph_paebinger_QGW_II_II_3637">Cristoforum
                        Päbinger, <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__nappersdorf-pfarre"><add>Pfarrer</add></roleName> in Napperstorff, parochialium
                        ecclesiarum rectores</rs> .</rs></rs>
            </p></div><div type="nota"><p><rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_II_3637"><rs type="fn" role="witness">Signet und
